---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Route One Model — Route One Advisory">
  <main class="min-h-dvh">
    
    <!-- Section: The Misdiagnosis -->
    <section class="px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-ro-green text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 fade-up">
          The Misdiagnosis
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-ro-text-bright leading-tight mb-6 fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
          You think you need to cut costs.<br />
          <span class="text-ro-gold">Actually, you have a leakage problem.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-lg text-ro-text fade-up fade-up-delay-2">
          <p>
            A VFX studio came to us ready to lay off half their team. Their EBITDA looked like it had collapsed from 22% to 4%. They were convinced the business was dying.
          </p>
          <p>
            We spent three weeks in their data. What we found: 
            <span class="text-ro-gold font-medium">Reported EBITDA was $0.6M. Actual EBITDA was $4.0M.</span>
          </p>
          <p>
            The $3.4M gap? Strategic investments coded as expenses. Pricing discipline erosion nobody was tracking. Productivity leaks that added up. One-time costs mixed into operating expenses.
          </p>
          <p>
            They didn't need a turnaround. They needed <span class="text-ro-text-bright font-medium">visibility</span>.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- EBITDA Bridge Visual -->
        <div class="mt-12 bg-ro-card border border-ro-card-border rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 fade-up fade-up-delay-3">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ro-text-bright mb-6">The Hidden EBITDA Bridge</h3>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-ro-text-dim">Reported EBITDA</span>
              <span class="text-ro-text-bright font-mono">$0.6M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-ro-green">
              <span>+ Strategic Investments</span>
              <span class="font-mono">$2.2M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-ro-green">
              <span>+ Operational Leakage</span>
              <span class="font-mono">$0.8M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between text-ro-green">
              <span>+ One-Time Costs</span>
              <span class="font-mono">$0.4M</span>
            </div>
            <div class="border-t border-ro-card-border pt-4 flex items-center justify-between">
              <span class="text-ro-gold font-semibold">Actual EBITDA</span>
              <span class="text-ro-gold font-mono font-bold text-xl">$4.0M</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="mt-6 text-ro-text-dim text-sm">
            This company went from planning layoffs to planning expansion. The only thing that changed was what they could see.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Section: The Model -->
    <section class="px-6 py-16 md:py-24 bg-ro-darker">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <p class="text-ro-green text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 fade-up">
            The Route One Model
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-ro-text-bright mb-4 fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
            We don't rent you employees.<br />
            We run your finance department.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-ro-text-dim max-w-2xl mx-auto fade-up fade-up-delay-2">
            One team. Full coverage. Guaranteed results.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Three Pillars -->
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
          <div class="bg-ro-card border border-ro-card-border rounded-xl p-6 fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-ro-green/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ro-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ro-text-bright mb-2">Core Accounting</h3>
            <p class="text-ro-text-dim text-sm">
              AP/AR, reconciliations, journal entries, month-end close. The foundation that keeps everything running.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-ro-card border border-ro-card-border rounded-xl p-6 fade-up fade-up-delay-2">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-ro-green/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ro-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17v-2m3 2v-4m3 4v-6m2 10H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ro-text-bright mb-2">Controllership</h3>
            <p class="text-ro-text-dim text-sm">
              Financial oversight, internal controls, audit readiness, reporting & performance insights.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-ro-card border border-ro-card-border rounded-xl p-6 fade-up fade-up-delay-3">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-ro-green/20 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-ro-green" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ro-text-bright mb-2">Strategic Finance</h3>
            <p class="text-ro-text-dim text-sm">
              Fractional CFO services, FP&A modeling, capital raise support, board-ready reporting.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Team Structure -->
        <div class="bg-ro-card border border-ro-card-border rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 fade-up fade-up-delay-4">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ro-text-bright mb-6 text-center">Your Full Department</h3>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-ro-green/20 text-ro-green rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Controller</span>
            <span class="text-ro-text-dim">→</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-ro-card-border/50 text-ro-text rounded-full text-sm">Accounting Manager</span>
            <span class="text-ro-text-dim">→</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-ro-card-border/50 text-ro-text rounded-full text-sm">Sr. Accountant</span>
            <span class="text-ro-text-dim">→</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-ro-card-border/50 text-ro-text rounded-full text-sm">Staff Accountant</span>
            <span class="text-ro-text-dim">→</span>
            <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-ro-card-border/50 text-ro-text rounded-full text-sm">Clerk</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-ro-text-dim text-sm text-center mt-6">
            All managed. All guaranteed. All for less than you'd pay a single domestic hire.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Section: Speed -->
    <section class="px-6 py-16 md:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <p class="text-ro-green text-sm font-medium tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 fade-up">
            How Fast We Move
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-ro-text-bright mb-4 fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
            Most clients are current within weeks, not months.
          </h2>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Timeline -->
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4 fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ro-green rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">1</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ro-text-bright">Rapid Onboarding</h3>
              <p class="text-ro-text-dim">Get you current. Clean up the backlog. Establish baseline visibility.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4 fade-up fade-up-delay-2">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ro-green/80 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">2</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ro-text-bright">Scale Operations</h3>
              <p class="text-ro-text-dim">Build out your team structure. Implement SOPs. Create repeatable processes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4 fade-up fade-up-delay-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ro-green/60 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">3</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ro-text-bright">Process Improvements</h3>
              <p class="text-ro-text-dim">AI-assisted GL coding. Automation. Continuous optimization.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4 fade-up fade-up-delay-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-ro-green/40 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-sm">4</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ro-text-bright">Enablement</h3>
              <p class="text-ro-text-dim">You step back. We run it. You get reports, not problems.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="px-6 py-16 md:py-24 bg-ro-darker">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-ro-text-bright mb-4 fade-up">
          Ready to meet the team behind this?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-ro-text-dim mb-8 fade-up fade-up-delay-1">
          Big Four rigor. Startup energy. No assholes.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="/talk"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-ro-green hover:bg-ro-green-light text-white text-lg font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded-lg transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ro-gold focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-ro-darker fade-up fade-up-delay-2"
        >
          Meet the Team
          <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
    
  </main>
</Layout>
